  "title": "Stress, Savings and Stability:",
  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<article>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--type--text--bleed paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div class=\"hero__container hero__container--small hero__container--no-image\" data-hero-container=\"\"><div class=\"container container--max-width\"><div class=\"hero__text-container hero__text-container--center hero__text-container__small\"><h1 class=\"u-font-family-secondary hero__title\">Stress, Savings and Stability:<br/>Reframing Life Insurance for Today's Families</h1></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p>Balancing the needs of both parents and children has become the new financial tightrope for millions. This course explores how life insurance can serve as a tool for stability amid mounting pressures of caregiving, rising costs, and delayed retirement. Examine why traditional coverage often falls short and learn how modern strategies such as hybrid life and long-term care products, living benefits, and policy laddering can bridge the gap. Through practical examples, gain insights into helping families create sustainable protection and peace of mind for generations to come.</p><table style=\"font-size:inherit;margin:32px 0;width:100%;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding-right:40px;vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Pricing</strong><br/>$49.00*</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Webinar Duration</strong><br/>60 minutes</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>CE Requirements</strong><br/><a href=\"https://web.theinstitutes.org/ceu/state-requirements\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Verify your state and license CE requirements</a></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<di