_item\"><dt class=\"detail-list__title\"><p>Topics</p></dt><dd class=\"detail-list__desc\"><ul><li>Explore the financial and emotional realities facing the Sandwich Generation</li><li>Examine gaps in traditional life insurance coverage and their long-term impact</li><li>Understand modern product innovations such as hybrid and living benefit options</li><li>Build client-centered strategies that balance affordability with protection</li><li>Learn to communicate value and legacy planning to enhance financial security </li></ul></dd></div></dl></div></article></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div style=\"margin:0 auto;max-width:1200px;text-align:center;\"><h3 style=\"margin-bottom:15px;\">Choose Your Date and Time</h3><div id=\"webinar-buttons\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;justify-content:center;\"><a class=\"btn btn--primary\" data-date=\"2026-04-15\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/stress-savings-and-stability-reframing-life-insurance-todays-families-20260415\" style=\"flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 16px);max-width:360px;min-width:260px;text-align:center;\">Wed, April 15 – 11:00 AM EST</a> <a class=\"btn btn--primary\" data-date=\"2026-05-05\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/stress-savings-and-stability-reframing-life-insurance-todays-families-20260505\" style=\"flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 16px);max-width:360px;min-width:260px;text-align:center;\">Tue, May 05 – 11:00 AM EST</a> </div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><section id=\"unlimited\"><hr/></section></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<section>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<article class=\"container__grid media-block__container media-block__container--reversed\">\n<div class=\"media-block__img-container\">\n<img alt=\"A pink pi